comments: Adebayo (MIA) firms up Hield's (PHI) path and absorbs the marginal contact as they come together during the pick.
Herro (MIA) legally contests Hield's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Martin (PHI) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Jaquez Jr.'s (MIA) arm as deflects the rebound away.
Martin (PHI) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Oubre Jr. (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Oubre Jr. jumps into and initiates contact with Highsmith's (MIA) lower body, which affects his ability to return to the floor after securing the rebound.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Jaquez Jr. (MIA) initiates contact with Reed's (PHI) right arm, which alters his play at the basket.
Payne (PHI) and Herro (MIA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Payne (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball during his steal attempt and Herro (MIA) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the 76ers.
Highsmith (MIA) moves alongside Maxey's (PHI) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending on Adebayo (MIA) is confirmed.  Adebayo makes contact with the ball after it reaches its apex and is on its downward flight toward the basket.
Reed (PHI) legally contests Robinson's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) avoids making any illegal contact with Jaquez Jr. (MIA) during the putback dunk attempt.
Robinson (MIA) delivers body contact to Maxey (PHI), which affects Maxey's SQBR as he starts his dribble.
After receiving the inbound pass, Adebayo (MIA) moves his pivot foot heel-to-toe to create distance prior to starting his dribble.
Herro (MIA) briefly grasps and immediately releases Hield's (PHI) right arm as marginal contact occurs during Herro's dribble on the perimeter.
Hield (PHI) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) and Martin (PHI) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs prior to Adebayo making clean contact with the ball to tap it away from Martin.
Hield (PHI) initiates illegal contact with Adebayo's (MIA) arm, which disrupts his dribble.
Martin (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Martin (PHI).
